            <div class="english-content">
                <h2>Introduction</h2>
                <p>
                    SDPMSS (SEWA DYA PARIYAR MANAWTA SEWA SASTHAN) values your support and trust. As we are just starting in the technology field, we currently do not provide any refunds or returns.
                </p>
                <h2>Refund and Return Policy</h2>
